Package index

Metadata

hochschulen
Hochschulen - Higher education institutions in Germany
tables
Student statistics tables ("21311 Statistik der Studenten")
metadata
Metadata containing the variables for each student statistics table
value_labels
Value labels for all variables in the student statistics tables
variable_info
Additional information and comments for some variables

Functions

clean_df()
Cleans column names, removes unwanted columns and turns data frame into a tibble.
col_to_url()
Converts a column with URL fragments into the full URL
document_format_section()
Get roxygen format section for a given table name
document_items()
Gets the item list for each table used in the roxygen documentation
document_table()
Get text for the R file documenting a table
document_title()
Get title for roxygen data table documentation
get_ncol()
Get formatted number of columns / variables in a data frame
get_nrow()
Get formatted number of rows in a data frame
get_table_name()
Takes table code or name as input and returns table name or code
label_values()
Set value labels using labelled::set_value_labels
label_variables()
Set variable labels using labelled::set_variable_labels
